{"tid":903883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【教練性侵案】田徑教練黃恆非禮女學員罪名不成立","createTime":"2018-11-16T02:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T02:24:22.000Z","uid":14918,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ead69be5b9e69f44556e4bbc98038292563bc9b","tid":903883,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:18:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181116&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58919187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181116%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58919187&d=MpvUtDhoU6d9xR18VsuFQ54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=44256604\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181116%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58919187&h=b4da08a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181116&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58919187</a><br />\n<br />\n曾任田徑教練的77歲退休人士黃恆，涉於8年前在大埔住所藉詞替女學員按摩，強扯對方內褲非禮，案件經審訊後，裁判官今裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n案審期間事主X在屏風後作供，指2009年9月1日至2010年4月8日期間某天在被告寓所，被告藉詞按摩雙腿要求她脫下長褲，並突然扯下她內褲在陰毛位置撫摸打圈。<br />\n<br />\n被告自辯時則稱，由於事主X當時身穿厚身牛仔褲，「好難攞到個感覺」，遂建議X脫下長褲，X同意。被告指先後替X按摩大腿和小腿肌肉，歷時約1小時，其間兩人有傾有講，「佢同我溝通可以按邊度邊度」。被告強調，X在整個按摩過程中均有穿內褲，他從沒扯下對方內褲。"},{"pid":"c1ded84967fd7d52fe3a4d505c8d525d71c6ae07","tid":903883,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"支持公開女事主全名"},{"pid":"b13e6211f81ec2251b3355583ebf716dcb072a82","tid":903883,"uid":56649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:24:22.000Z","msg":"係人都知x係邊個啦<br />\n下次再屈過第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢識個d男士<br />\n自己小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}